25:48.881 --> 25:52.416
I need to get back to Adam
to fill him in on what I found.

25:52.418 --> 25:55.986
♪♪

25:55.988 --> 25:59.256
So, the mirror, they believe,
came from an estate sale

25:59.258 --> 26:00.824
that was at Collins Farm.

26:00.826 --> 26:03.794
So, I started doing some digging
on the Collins family.

26:03.796 --> 26:05.496
There were a lot of kids
in that family,

26:05.498 --> 26:08.699
but one of the kids,
Clarence Collins,

