So, the murder happened
October 17, 1918.
Mm-hmm.

26:47.440 --> 26:50.341
They were both executed
in 1921.

26:50.343 --> 26:52.876
Mm-hmm.
So, not long after the crime
was committed.

26:52.878 --> 26:55.245
The crazy thing is,
like I said, that mirror

26:55.247 --> 26:58.048
